<div class="article-header">

    






    
    
    
    
        
    








    
        <h1 class="isFirstInSlot">
            For jobs and the econ­o­my: Im­me­di­ate As­sis­tance Pro­gramme and Eco­nom­ic Sta­bil­i­sa­tion Fund<span/>
        </h1>
    

    

    
        <div class="subheadline">
<p class="heading">
<span>Financial assistance to mitigate the effects of the coronavirus pandemic: You can find up-to-date information here on various types of financial assistance for employees, freelancers, self-employed individuals and companies of all sizes.</span></p>
</div>
    

    
    

    

    
</div>





                        
                        













                    
                
            </div>
        </div>
